{A modern super-GM showcase (Volokitin 2660, Ivanchuk 2731). Ivanchuk handles the
Exchange Variation with deep maneuvering, reroutes his knights onto strong squares,
and slowly squeezes until White's position collapses. The Alekhine alive and well in
the 2700 era.}
